text: The Andorran Football Federation (; FAF) is the governing body of football in Andorra. It organizes the football league Primera Divisió, the Copa Constitució and Andorran Supercup and the Andorra national football team. The association was founded in 1994. It became a member of FIFA and UEFA in 1996.
